<h2>Welcome to WebLinDa</h2>

<p>WebLinDa is a inter-linear gloss system designed for collecting and collaboratively editing linguistic field data.</p>

<p>WebLinDa has data collected for the following languages:</p>
<ul>
<% @languages.each do |language| %>
	<li><%= link_to language, language_path(language) %></li>
<% end %>	
</ul>

